{"tid":880606,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李斯特城證實：班主維猜直升機墜毀意外中罹難","createTime":"2018-10-28T23:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T00:13:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48a34702cea48727c832c7bdb206b02607968842","tid":880606,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T23:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181029/large/1540765083_1dc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181029%2Flarge%2F1540765083_1dc4.jpg&h=09c00a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李斯特城周日發表聲明，證實班主維猜（Vichai Srivaddhanaprabha）在上周六晚直升機墜毀意外中死亡。聲明透露，維猜與直升機上的另外四人，包括兩名機員和兩名維猜的下屬全部罹難。<br />\n<br />\n李城上周六晚主場賽和韋斯咸的英超比賽後，屬於維猜的直升機在球場外停車場墜毀，墜地時發出巨響並且着火，事發一日後李城終發表聲明證實維猜罹難。<br />\n<br />\n李城在聲明中表示，懷著深切的悲痛和遺憾證實，主席維猜是周六晚直升機在皇權球場外墜毀事件的遇難者之一，機上五人無人生還。聲明並指出，這個世界失去了一個偉大的人，一個善良、慷慨以及其生命是由他獻給家庭的愛和那些他如此成功地領導的人所界定的人。李斯特城是一個由他領導的大家庭，作為一個家庭，我們會為他的逝世而悲痛，並會繼續追求現在已成為其遺產的球會的願景。"},{"pid":"69b491540d0770de5bca702a0a1e22a6e248646e","tid":880606,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T23:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181029/58847642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58847642&d=1Fqst2YE4s9YKDTYceK5OaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=1051ae0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58847642&h=60433a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181029/58847642</a>"},{"pid":"36afd05a6da56129bf074e10b4db8280536a765d","tid":880606,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T23:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2c913f6f54f6965ba154c1d721100f